    # cw "I'll be okay. Let's go. I just want to leave."
    cw "我没事的。走吧。我只想离开这里。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:325
translate chinese dana13rescue_eb41928b:

    # "She fills a small bag with some things and then we leave the house together."
