translate chinese dana13rescue_608a1253:

    # cw "I'll be right back, I need to go use your bathroom."
    cw "我马上回来，我得去用一下你的洗手间。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:404
translate chinese dana13rescue_82996611:

    # "Liz" "Of course. My casa is your casa."
    "Liz" "当然。我家就是你家。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:407
translate chinese dana13rescue_ebba3463:

    # "When Dana closes the door, Liz rushes towards me and pulls me into a surprisingly strong hug."
    "达娜关上门后，莉兹立刻冲过来，用出乎意料的力气把我搂进怀里。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:408
translate chinese dana13rescue_827c7e1a:

    # "Liz" "Oh my God, thank you for saving her. I could kiss you."
    "Liz" "天哪，谢谢你救了她。真想亲你一下。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:409
translate chinese dana13rescue_ef6ddb4a:

    # pc "I didn't really do much. He was just like a baby throwing a fit."
    pc "我其实没做什么。他就像个发脾气的孩子。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:412
translate chinese dana13rescue_cd9db1c9:

    # "Liz" "I don't just mean today. Thank you for saving her from that marriage."
    "Liz" "我不是只说今天的事。谢谢你把她从那段婚姻里解救出来。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:413
translate chinese dana13rescue_dd45aad4:

    # "Liz" "She would have been stuck with that asshole forever if you hadn't shown her something better."
    "Liz" "要不是你让她看到了更好的选择，她恐怕得永远被那个混蛋困住。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:414
translate chinese dana13rescue_5eba77d8:

    # "Liz" "So do you really care about her or are you just fucking her?"
    "Liz" "所以你是真心在乎她，还是只是跟她上床？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:417
translate chinese dana13rescue_108615b9:

    # "Liz" "Good. I like you, [pcname]. I know we haven't met, but she's been telling me about you for weeks."
    "Liz" "好。我喜欢你，[pcname]。虽然我们没见过面，但她已经跟我聊了你好几周了。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:418
translate chinese dana13rescue_1d541d19:

    # "Liz" "I think you're going to be good for her."
    "Liz" "我觉得你会对她很好的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:419
translate chinese dana13rescue_13818456:

    # "Liz" "So be good for her, okay?"
    "Liz" "那就对她好点，行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:420
translate chinese dana13rescue_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "我会的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:423
translate chinese dana13rescue_63d61538:

    # "Liz" "Nothing wrong with that. Just make sure she knows it."
    "Liz" "这没什么不对的。只要确保她知道就好。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:424
translate chinese dana13rescue_f3ea1ea3:

    # "Liz" "Don't hurt her, okay?"
    "Liz" "别伤害她，行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:425
translate chinese dana13rescue_dd9a629d:

    # pc "I won't."
    pc "我不会的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:428
translate chinese dana13rescue_c661e3b4:

    # "Liz" "She wasn't lying about how cute you are, that's for sure."
    "Liz" "她没说谎，你确实很可爱，这点毋庸置疑。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:429
translate chinese dana13rescue_49ab107b:

    # "Liz" "Why don't you go sit down and I'll make us a snack."
    "Liz" "你先去坐下，我来给我们做点零食。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:432
translate chinese dana13rescue_145580ef:

    # "I go sit on the couch while she starts popping popcorn in the kitchen."
    "我坐在沙发上，她则在厨房里开始爆玉米花。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:433
translate chinese dana13rescue_9d498b37:

    # "A few minutes later, Dana walks out of the bathroom and comes over to join me."
    "几分钟后，达娜从浴室走出来，过来坐在我身边。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:436
translate chinese dana13rescue_c8e1e27b:

    # "She sits and leans up against me. I put an arm around her and pull her close."
    "她坐下，靠在我身上。我搂住她，把她拉近。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:437
translate chinese dana13rescue_c5847b6b:

    # pc "You okay?"
    pc "你还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:439
translate chinese dana13rescue_d41d8cd9_17:

    # voice "voices/dana 12_23.wav"
    voice "voices/dana 12_23.wav"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:440
translate chinese dana13rescue_ad095c3c:

    # cw "I will be. Can you just stay and hold me for a while?"
    cw "我会的。你能留下来抱抱我一会儿吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:441
translate chinese dana13rescue_08551511:

    # pc "You got it."
    pc "没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:444
translate chinese dana13rescue_0fefcb7d:

    # "Liz brings the popcorn over and sits on the other side of Dana."
    "莉兹端着爆米花过来，坐在达娜的另一侧。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:445
translate chinese dana13rescue_7d2b023d:

    # "Liz" "Want to watch something?"
    "Liz" "想看点什么吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:447
translate chinese dana13rescue_d41d8cd9_18:

    # voice "voices/dana 12_24.wav"
    voice "voices/dana 12_24.wav"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:448
translate chinese dana13rescue_e90dd285:

    # cw "Yeah, put on one of your dumb kung-fu movies."
    cw "嗯，放你那些傻乎乎的功夫片吧。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:449
translate chinese dana13rescue_e6dfa26a:

    # pc "You like kung-fu movies?"
    pc "你喜欢功夫片吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:451
translate chinese dana13rescue_d41d8cd9_19:

    # voice "voices/dana 12_25.wav"
    voice "voices/dana 12_25.wav"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:452
translate chinese dana13rescue_8b49506a:

    # cw "She loves them."
    cw "她超爱看。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:453
translate chinese dana13rescue_5cbaa3c7:

    # pc "Me too!"
    pc "我也是！"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:459
translate chinese dana13rescue_6f86ff9e:

    # "Liz puts on an old Jackie Chan movie. I'd already seen it before, but we just chit-chat about other kung-fu movies while we all cuddle together on the couch."
    "莉兹放了一部老版的成龙电影。 虽然我之前看过这部，但我们还是挤在沙发上依偎着，闲聊起其他功夫电影。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:460
translate chinese dana13rescue_f28cc975:

    # "Dana doesn't talk much, but she seems to be enjoying herself at least, letting the drama of the night wash away from her."
    "达娜没说什么话，但至少看起来很开心，仿佛今晚的种种波折都随风而逝。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:463
translate chinese dana13rescue_5723d838:

    # "By the end of the movie, Dana is fast asleep, snoring lightly against me."
    "电影结束时，达娜已经睡着了，轻声打着呼噜靠在我身上。"

