translate chinese dana13rescue_880efdd6:

    # "I'm feeling pretty tired too, my eyelids heavy."
    "我也挺累的，眼皮沉甸甸的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:467
translate chinese dana13rescue_8b1422d5:

    # "Liz" "Well, I guess we better hit the hay."
    "Liz" "嗯， 我想我们还是该上床睡觉了。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:468
translate chinese dana13rescue_3226b3be:

    # "Liz" "Dana, it's time for bed, honey."
    "Liz" "达娜，该睡觉了，亲爱的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:471
translate chinese dana13rescue_b0fcae85:

    # "Dana groggily turns towards me and kisses me on the lips."
    "达娜迷迷糊糊地转过身来，亲了亲我的嘴唇。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:472
translate chinese dana13rescue_46ba0430:

    # "Liz" "You can stay too if you want, [pcname]. The couch is pretty comfortable."
    "Liz" "如果你愿意的话也可以留下来，[pcname]。沙发挺舒服的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:475
translate chinese dana13rescue_e7cf003b:

    # pc "Yeah, I think I will. I'm a little too tired to drive home."
    pc "嗯，我想我会留下的。我太累了，没力气开车回家。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:476
translate chinese dana13rescue_894b4e6d:

    # "Liz" "I'll get you a blanket."
    "Liz" "我给你拿条毯子。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:478
translate chinese dana13rescue_d41d8cd9_20:

    # voice "voices/dana 12_26.wav"
    voice "voices/dana 12_26.wav"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:479
translate chinese dana13rescue_cbdf500d:

    # cw "Night-night, [pcname]."
    cw "晚安，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:480
translate chinese dana13rescue_db6f9f89:

    # pc "Good night, Dana."
    pc "晚安，达娜。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:483
translate chinese dana13rescue_fe853434:

    # "I go to the bathroom to get ready for bed and when I come back out, Liz has placed a blanket on the couch for me."
    "我去浴室准备睡觉，回来时，莉兹已经给我铺好了沙发上的毯子。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:484
translate chinese dana13rescue_cc210ada:

    # "I take off my clothes, lie down, and fall asleep almost immediately."
    "我脱掉衣服，躺下，几乎立刻就睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:488
translate chinese dana13rescue_529a1d9f:

    # "I'm not sure what time it is when a weight on top of me wakes me up. It takes me a moment to remember where I am and recognize Dana's form."
    "我不确定是什么时候，身上的一股重量把我弄醒了。我花了一会儿才想起来自己身在何处，认出了达娜的身影。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana13.rpy:489
translate chinese dana13rescue_a337c6a3:

